      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662119\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMatteID</a> outputs matte AOVs for compositing.  This requires you add a User Attribute, explained in more detail <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643715/User+Attributes\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"fdef2b2d-b4bc-4ecf-8c6b-64b17bc39cbe\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>PxrCryptomatte has since superseded this workflow as a useful and nearly automatic alternative.</p></div></div><hr/><p /><h3 id=\"UsingPxrMatteID-AddauserattributeforMatteID0.\">Add a user attribute for MatteID0.</h3><p>Duplicate the fields for:</p><ul><li><p>Name</p></li><li><p>Label (this is the UI name)</p></li><li><p>Tags (necessary to see RenderMan attributes and edit them during interactive rendering)<br/>script_ritype  color<br/>renderman  attr</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_addMatteUserAttrEdit.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1115&amp;height=786\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646676/rfh_addMatteUserAttrEdit.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"786\" data-width=\"1115\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646713\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_addMatteUserAttrEdit.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646676\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c97c1f35-2d34-49d0-9318-5ab1405491d8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_addMatteUserAttrEdit.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1115&amp;height=786 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_addMatteUserAttrEdit.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157394&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1115&amp;height=786 1x\"></span><p>Set its type and color value.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/sphereuserattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=715&amp;height=298\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646676/sphereuserattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"298\" data-width=\"715\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646695\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"sphereuserattrib.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646676\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7aa7cf20-bb43-43d5-8186-d21425641b7f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/sphereuserattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=715&amp;height=298 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/sphereuserattrib.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433156972&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=715&amp;height=298 1x\"></span><p /><h3 id=\"UsingPxrMatteID-AddPxrMatteID\">Add PxrMatteID</h3><p>Create a Houdini buildarray node to connect to the Utility Pattern on the PxrSurface material. Then connect a PxrMatteID Pattern node to the buildarray as shown below.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_matteIDArrayNode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=748\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646676/rfh_matteIDArrayNode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"748\" data-width=\"868\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646707\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_matteIDArrayNode.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646676\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"47ffdc5c-6d2d-45b4-9a78-f6d4686efc36\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_matteIDArrayNode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=748 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_matteIDArrayNode.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=748 1x\"></span><p /><p>In your PxrMaterialBuilder Network, add a PxrMatteID VOP.  Set the color as the user attribute above.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/pxrmatteid.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=717&amp;height=364\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646676/pxrmatteid.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"364\" data-width=\"717\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646701\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrmatteid.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646676\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7e0e07e6-d363-4428-a320-ced1a9ea699a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/pxrmatteid.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=717&amp;height=364 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/pxrmatteid.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=717&amp;height=364 1x\"></span><p /><p /><p>Connect PxrMatteID's resultAOV to PxrSurface's Utility Pattern.</p><h3 id=\"UsingPxrMatteID-SetupAOVforOutput\">Set up AOV for Output</h3><p>Choose the correct/corresponding MatteID AOV output from the RenderMan ROP node Displays Tab</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1141\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_matteIDOutput.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=816\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646676/rfh_matteIDOutput.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"816\" data-width=\"868\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646704\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_matteIDOutput.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646676\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"36c87fdd-d998-4fa1-af3b-c8db59372153\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_matteIDOutput.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=816 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646676/rfh_matteIDOutput.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157217&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=868&amp;height=816 1x\"></span><p /><p>You will notice we set a color on the OBJ with an attribute and there's also a color from the MatteID pattern itself. This is so you can multiply the color of the attribute by the pattern node. For example, you can supply a texture mask to the MatteID pattern node and have it multiplied against the color chosen in the MatteID Attribute</p><p /><p /><p /><p />"
    }
  },
